At Fruit & Veggie Health, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy outlines the types of information we collect, how we use and safeguard that information, and your rights regarding your data. By using this extension, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect
Fruit & Veggie Health does not collect any personal information or sensitive data from users. We do not require or request personal details such as names, email addresses, or location data.

2. How We Use Information
This extension operates locally on your browser. All data such as search queries and preferences are stored on your device and not transmitted to any external servers. The primary purpose of this extension is to provide nutritional information about fruits and vegetables, and it functions without needing any form of data collection.

3. Cookies and Tracking Technologies
This extension does not use any cookies or tracking technologies. No browsing data, usage logs, or personal information are stored or shared.

4. Third-Party Links
Our extension may provide links to external websites (e.g., AskBart.Org) for further information. These third-party websites may have their own privacy policies, which we recommend reviewing, as we are not responsible for their content or privacy practices.

5. Security
While our extension does not collect personal data, we are committed to ensuring that your information and experience remain private and secure. Since no data is collected or transmitted, there is no risk of external interception.

6. Children's Privacy
This extension is not directed to individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect any data from children under 13.

7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be reflected on this page with an updated revision date at the top. By continuing to use the extension after these changes take effect, you agree to the revised policy.

8. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the extension, please feel free to contact us at:

Email: support@askbart.org
Website: https://askbart.org
